{"ID":"afdde70f-f09a-4c59-84c4-40388bbba08b","VersionNumber":0,"Name":"Production Databases not in FULL recovery mode","Description":"<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\r\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\r\n\t<head>\r\n\t\t<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" /><title>\r\n\t\t</title>\r\n\t\t<style type=\"text/css\">\r\n\t\t\t.cs2654AE3A{text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt}\r\n\t\t\t.csBEC5BAA2{color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:8pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;}\r\n\t\t\t.cs6BD174F1{color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:8pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-decoration: none;}\r\n\t\t\t.csC1A17A41{color:#0000FF;background-color:transparent;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:8pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-decoration: underline;}\r\n\t\t</style>\r\n\t</head>\r\n\t<body>\r\n\t\t<p class=\"cs2654AE3A\"><span class=\"csBEC5BAA2\">A daily check to ensure that production databases on production servers are in the full recovery mode to reduce the risk of data loss.</span></p><p class=\"cs2654AE3A\"><span class=\"csBEC5BAA2\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"cs2654AE3A\"><span class=\"csBEC5BAA2\">Please do not enable this alert at the global level if you are also monitoring development instances as this could provide false positives.</span></p><p class=\"cs2654AE3A\"><span class=\"csBEC5BAA2\">It is suggested that you create groups within the Navigator window and have production servers within those groups. Set this aert at the group level where it makes sense to do so.</span></p><p class=\"cs2654AE3A\"><span class=\"csBEC5BAA2\">You can read more about how hierachies work here - <a class=\"cs6BD174F1\" href=\"https://docs.sentryone.com/help/alerting-and-responses-overview#alerting-and-response-system-hierarchy\"><span class=\"csC1A17A41\">https://docs.sentryone.com/help/alerting-and-responses-overview#alerting-and-response-system-hierarchy</span></a></span></p><p class=\"cs2654AE3A\"><span class=\"csBEC5BAA2\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"cs2654AE3A\"><span class=\"csBEC5BAA2\">If you wish to exclude extra databases fromn these checks they can be added into the query below or in the Condition settings for the alert itself.</span></p><p class=\"cs2654AE3A\"><span class=\"csBEC5BAA2\">The query below already excldes TempDB and ReportServerTempDB which are in simple mode by default.</span></p><p class=\"cs2654AE3A\"><span class=\"csBEC5BAA2\">&nbsp;</span></p></body>\r\n</html>\r\n","AppliesToObjectTypeID":"0a11a887-823a-4461-87af-321cad1c3623","ConditionCategoryID":"805a84c9-7f1b-4b4d-a9ad-3dddcf9e0f17","OwnerObjectID":"b7c74f24-1a45-4115-8262-d7613878bbd6","OwnerObjectTypeID":"894de672-3fc0-4779-9a0d-880d4c207c77","RuleDefinition":"{\"OperationTypeID\":\"6c3d38f1-9317-4258-972a-cfee0a0d76b5\",\"Children\":[{\"OperationTypeID\":\"8fa3cd6a-960c-43bb-96e0-94092fc2c296\",\"ValueDataTypeID\":\"edef9757-3766-460b-a15c-8dd529304229\",\"Left\":{\"ValueTypeID\":\"f2e88d72-73c6-4ce1-b92a-029c313e707f\",\"Query\":\"SELECT esc.ServerName+':'+ pasd.name \\r\\nFROM [dbo].[PerformanceAnalysisSqlDatabase] pasd\\r\\nINNER JOIN dbo.EventSourceConnection esc\\r\\n\\tON pasd.EventSourceConnectionID = esc.ID\\r\\nWHERE pasd.RecoveryModel <> 3\\r\\nAND pasd.name NOT IN ('TempDB', 'ReportServerTempDB')\\r\\nAND esc.ID = @ConnectionID\",\"InstanceType\":0},\"ComparisonType\":1,\"Right\":{\"ValueTypeID\":\"07f87b7f-c063-47a2-a5be-772ba85ed827\",\"Value\":\"NULL\"},\"ID\":\"1\"}],\"BooleanOperationType\":0,\"ID\":\"0\"}","EvaluationFrequency":"1.00:00:00","IdlePeriod":"00:00:00","MaximumAllowedDuration":"00:00:05","AntiConditionID":"92ecf90d-5e96-4e5a-abb9-ce35758bb0a8","MinWindowsVersion":null,"MaxWindowsVersion":null,"MinSQLServerVersion":null,"MaxSQLServerVersion":null,"MinSSASVersion":null,"MaxSSASVersion":null,"MinVmwareVersion":null,"MaxVmwareVersion":null,"MinSqlDbVersion":null,"MaxSqlDbVersion":null,"MaximumInstanceCount":100,"ColorIndicator":-65536,"Severity":2,"Signature":{"ConditionID":"afdde70f-f09a-4c59-84c4-40388bbba08b","VersionNumber":0,"AppliesToObjectTypeID":"0a11a887-823a-4461-87af-321cad1c3623","RuleDefinition":"{\"OperationTypeID\":\"6c3d38f1-9317-4258-972a-cfee0a0d76b5\",\"Children\":[{\"OperationTypeID\":\"8fa3cd6a-960c-43bb-96e0-94092fc2c296\",\"ValueDataTypeID\":\"edef9757-3766-460b-a15c-8dd529304229\",\"Left\":{\"ValueTypeID\":\"f2e88d72-73c6-4ce1-b92a-029c313e707f\",\"Query\":\"SELECT esc.ServerName+':'+ pasd.name \\r\\nFROM [dbo].[PerformanceAnalysisSqlDatabase] pasd\\r\\nINNER JOIN dbo.EventSourceConnection esc\\r\\n\\tON pasd.EventSourceConnectionID = esc.ID\\r\\nWHERE pasd.RecoveryModel <> 3\\r\\nAND pasd.name NOT IN ('TempDB', 'ReportServerTempDB')\\r\\nAND esc.ID = @ConnectionID\",\"InstanceType\":0},\"ComparisonType\":1,\"Right\":{\"ValueTypeID\":\"07f87b7f-c063-47a2-a5be-772ba85ed827\",\"Value\":\"NULL\"},\"ID\":\"1\"}],\"BooleanOperationType\":0,\"ID\":\"0\"}","PublisherID":0,"PublishDateUtc":"2021-02-17T11:49:57","Rights":0,"SignatureVersion":1,"SignaturePublicKey":"<RSAKeyValue><Modulus>uzJQ9gzevXFwOgw/hkcAtD+cA/bBbD1PRzhEZCxbZ6YwjJ1c9bbfXFItLQNwnm8bdWh2k57//qbpEj5DFHOW2EAjHc2Zw5m/vACm6OzelubPS5hbWvzshlaBJKm7KrpWQpPZClx/5eVvUVzOtlz+44RRTiOszObT58acJAQwA70=</Modulus><Exponent>AQAB</Exponent></RSAKeyValue>","Signature":"Q14gzjv0yc/s3I5lbsW8Mzncf4Fs9LYSHMR0gcAt5vDRQTd86ksQNWJNvBna10g4RvoGZgfn6ytyonOMsWnEZanz9LNKlquWpTSBjRZ2KOz10Qdtr1ew3LFnMmdqhzuB5EpmyqtGEG4t8UcU6CCXUd0G0ejfsBSjAz5BzLi3RIw=","IsSelfPublishedCondition":true},"Tags":"LRD,Business Continuity","Areas":["SQL Server: Backup MB/sec"],"ConditionSystemVersion":3,"MinDBSchemaVersion":null,"MaxDBSchemaVersion":null,"Items":[]}